1) ——> Install Bluemix CLI 

http://clis.ng.bluemix.net/ui/home.html

2) --> Login to Bluemix using your preferred region (US, Germany, UK, Sydney)

bx login -a https://api.ng.bluemix.net
			      https://api.eu-de.bluemix.net
		      	https://api.eu-gb.bluemix.net
			      https://api.au-syd.bluemix.net

3) --> Set organization and space 

    bx target -o Your_ORG -s Your_SPACE
            
4) —> Check installed plugin, install if necessary 
  
    bx plugin list
    if (empty or container service not installed execute command below)
      bx plugin install container-service

5) —> Initialize container service

    bx cs init
